# All That Glitters — Project Overview

Interactive fiction game built on **Twine 2 + SugarCube 2**. Adult-oriented slice-of-life with character relationships, jobs, quests, time-based schedules, wardrobe, phone OS, and map navigation.

## Tech Stack

- **Story engine:** SugarCube 2 (Twine 2 format)
- **Build tool:** Tweego (assumed) — reads `.twee` files under `passages/`
- **UI library:** jQuery (bundled with SugarCube)
- **Style:** Vanilla CSS with `:root` custom properties, no preprocessor
- **Asset pipeline:** `assets/system/config.js` declares JS/CSS module load order
- **AI image generation:** Python scripts under `Automation/FalNanoBanana2/` (FAL.AI) and `Automation/ReplicateBulk/` (Replicate)

