## Key Conventions

- **Language:** Code + commits in Turkish; passage text primarily English; rules files in English for agent consistency
- **File naming:** camelCase passages (`dinerRubysKitchen`), PascalCase widget files (`PhoneWidgets.twee`)
- **Variable scope:** `$` = story (persists), `_` = temporary (passage), `setup.` = static data
- **Never use** `<<endscript>>` — always `<</script>>` (SugarCube 2)
- **Always pair** `<<nobr>>` with `<</nobr>>` inside widgets
